        <item>
            <title><![CDATA[BCD New Universal Implementations Report, Mon May 25 2026]]></title>
            <link>https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/weekly-completed/2026-05-25.html</link>
            <guid>https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/weekly-completed/2026-05-25.html</guid>
            <pubDate>Mon, 25 May 2026 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
            <description><![CDATA[Weekly summary of new Baseline items in BCD data]]></description>
            <content:encoded><![CDATA[<main>
    <p>
	Summary of BCD changes from <a href=""><time title="Monday, 18 May 2026">Monday, 18 May 2026</time></a> through <time title="Monday, 25 May 2026">Monday, 25 May 2026</time></strong><a href="https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/weekly-completed/2026-05-25.html" title="permalink">🔗</a>
    </p>
    <hr>


          <p class="callout"><strong>8 new universal implementations</strong></p>
          <section class="added implementations">
	            <h4>API</h4>
              <ol>
                  <li>

          

                      <span>
                        <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/Element/requestPointerLock#unadjustedmovement">api ➞ Element ➞ requestPointerLock ➞ options_unadjustedMovement_parameter</a>
                      </span>
                    
                    <b><br></b> 
                    <span class="browsers">Added to <strong>Firefox</strong></span> 
                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>
                    <span class="ni3 engines"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>

                  </li>
                  <li>
                      <span>api ➞ MathMLElement ➞ nonce
                      	<a href="https://html.spec.whatwg.org/multipage/urls-and-fetching.html#dom-noncedelement-nonce"><img src="https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/imgs/spec2.svg" alt="Spec link"></a>
                      </span>

          

                    
                    <b><br></b> 
                    <span class="browsers">Added to <strong>Firefox</strong></span> 
                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>
                    <span class="ni3 engines"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>

                  </li>
                  <li>

          

                      <span>
                        <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/finalResponseHeadersStart">api ➞ PerformanceResourceTiming ➞ finalResponseHeadersStart</a>
                      </span>
                    
                    <b><br></b> 
                    <span class="browsers">Added to <strong>Firefox</strong></span> 
                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>
                    <span class="ni3 engines"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>

                  </li>
                  <li>

          

                      <span>
                        <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/API/PerformanceResourceTiming/firstInterimResponseStart">api ➞ PerformanceResourceTiming ➞ firstInterimResponseStart</a>
                      </span>
                    
                    <b><br></b> 
                    <span class="browsers">Added to <strong>Firefox</strong></span> 
                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>
                    <span class="ni3 engines"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>

                  </li>
                  <li>
                      <span>api ➞ RTCPeerConnection ➞ RTCPeerConnection ➞ configuration_rtcpMuxPolicy_parameter
                      	<a href="https://w3c.github.io/webrtc-pc/#dom-rtcconfiguration-rtcpmuxpolicy"><img src="https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/imgs/spec2.svg" alt="Spec link"></a>
                      </span>

          

                    
                    <b><br></b> 
                    <span class="browsers">Added to <strong>Firefox</strong></span> 
                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>
                    <span class="ni3 engines"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>

                  </li>
              </ol>
	            <h4>CSS</h4>
              <ol>
                  <li>

          

                      <span>
                        <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/docs/Web/CSS/Reference/Properties/field-sizing">css ➞ properties ➞ field-sizing</a>
                      </span>
                    
                    <b><br></b> 
                    <span class="browsers">Added to <strong>Firefox</strong></span> 
                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>
                    <span class="ni3 engines"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>

                  </li>
                  <li>
                      <span>css ➞ properties ➞ field-sizing ➞ content
                      	<a href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-forms-1/#valdef-field-sizing-content"><img src="https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/imgs/spec2.svg" alt="Spec link"></a>
                      </span>

          

                    
                    <b><br></b> 
                    <span class="browsers">Added to <strong>Firefox</strong></span> 
                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>
                    <span class="ni3 engines"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>

                  </li>
                  <li>
                      <span>css ➞ properties ➞ field-sizing ➞ fixed
                      	<a href="https://drafts.csswg.org/css-forms-1/#valdef-field-sizing-fixed"><img src="https://bcd-watch.igalia.com/imgs/spec2.svg" alt="Spec link"></a>
                      </span>

          

                    
                    <b><br></b> 
                    <span class="browsers">Added to <strong>Firefox</strong></span> 
                    <b>&nbsp;➞&nbsp;</b>
                    <span class="ni3 engines"><strong>3 of 3</strong> engines</span>

                  </li>
              </ol>
          </section>

  <hr>
  <ul id="prev-next">
  	<li>Previous report: <a href=""><time title="Monday, 18 May 2026">Monday, 18 May 2026</time></a></li>
  </ul>
  <hr>
